66
00:04:59,519 --> 00:05:00,079
[SPEAKER_01] Bogu fala.

67
00:05:00,399 --> 00:05:02,240
[SPEAKER_01] Kupila sam sve kistove, sve sam kupila.

68
00:05:02,480 --> 00:05:03,279
